# astrion-skill v1
goal: Lock the screen immediately
trigger:
  - phrase: "lock"
  - phrase: "lock screen"
  - phrase: "lock the computer"
do: |
  Show the lock-screen overlay via the existing lock-screen.js module
  (emit 'screen:lock' on the event bus). The session state persists —
  reopening requires the account password. Skip if lock-screen is
  already visible.
constraints:
  level: L1
  budget_tokens: 80
  reversibility: FREE
